- A table with the following columns: Date, Conta, Categ, Tags, Note, Tax in UAH, Net in UAH, Amount in UAH, Tax 20%, Tax 7%
- A search bar at the top right corner
- A button "Attach documents" at the bottom left corner
- A button "Formatted" at the bottom right corner
- A button "Save as PDF..." at the bottom right corner
- A button "..." at the bottom right corner
- A checkbox "Show sums" in the Options section
- A checkbox "Show + signs" in the Options section
- A checkbox "Landscape" in the Options section
- A checkbox "Reference" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Date" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Paid" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Category" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Tags" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Title" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Note" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Export File Name" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Currency" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Tax in UAH" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Net in UAH" in the Columns section
- A checkbox "Amount in UAH" in the Columns section
- A button "Cancel" at the bottom left corner
- A button "Print..." at the bottom right corner